!====================================================
! METEODIAG: cyclone and jet identification
!====================================================

1. COMPILATION
   - adjust Makefile to your needs
   - type gmake

2. If you want a different grid, create grid file with desired pressure levels
   - create mygrid.cdl
   - run ncgen -b -o grid_meteodiag.nc mygrid.cdl

3. RUN
   - type ./meteodiag.exe meteodiag.nml


